title: 26-year-old woman charged with manslaughter in fatal shoving of 87-year-old Broadway vocal coach - CNN
content:

description: A 26-year-old woman was charged Tuesday with one count of first-degree manslaughter and two counts of second-degree assault in connection with the death of an 87-year-old woman who was fatally shoved in New York City earlier this month, according to a criminal complaint.
